        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Expose heartbeat template doctor lint findings",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add a default-disabled `core/doctor/heartbeat-template` structured health check for legacy `HEARTBEAT.md` documentation-template wrappers\n- reuse the existing heartbeat template analyzer so lint and legacy Doctor repair classify the same file shapes\n- keep actual replacement in the existing `doctor --fix` path; lint only reads and reports findings\n- no config, plugin, SDK, persisted data, or repair-path contract changes\n\n## Real behavior proof\n- Source CLI with isolated `OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH`, `OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR`, and workspace containing a legacy fenced `HEARTBEAT.md` template:\n  - `node scripts/run-node.mjs doctor --lint --json` ran broad default lint with `heartbeat=0`, proving default lint skips the new default-disabled check\n  - `node scripts/run-node.mjs doctor --lint --json --only core/doctor/heartbeat-template` ran `checksRun=1`, `checksSkipped=36`, emitted one `core/doctor/heartbeat-template` warning with `requirement: \"legacy-template\"`, and exited 1\n- Focused source harness proves pure dirty templates, dirty templates with user content, clean templates, and missing heartbeat files.\n\n## Validation\n- `PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false pnpm exec oxlint src/commands/doctor-heartbeat-template-repair.ts src/commands/doctor-heartbeat-template-repair.test.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.test.ts`\n- `PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false pnpm exec oxfmt --check src/commands/doctor-heartbeat-template-repair.ts src/commands/doctor-heartbeat-template-repair.test.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.test.ts`\n- `PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/commands/doctor-heartbeat-template-repair.test.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.test.ts`\n- `PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false pnpm tsgo:core`\n- `PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false node scripts/plugin-sdk-surface-report.mjs --check`\n- `PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false node scripts/sync-plugin-sdk-exports.mjs --check`\n- `git diff --check`\n",
